  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"id-1.20.1-NewFeatures\"><strong>New Features</strong></h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/kb/view/1938030615\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inventory Update Reasons</a> help managers track inventory by requiring staff to record the reason the item has been placed in defective status.</p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/kb/view/1951694865\" rel=\"nofollow\">Part Core Recovery</a> enables stores to recover and track parts that can be sent back to the manufacturer for reimbursement or credit.</p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/kb/view/1933246822\" rel=\"nofollow\">Appointment settings</a> have been streamlined and <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/kb/view/1953595423\" rel=\"nofollow\">Availability settings</a> help manage your appointments during peak times.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.20.1-BugFixesandImprovements\"><strong>Bug Fixes and Improvements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Fixed a permissions issue when updating the Supplier SKU field in a Purchase Order.</p></li><li><p>Fixed a conflict with the Location Admin and Location Advisor roles.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue with Brightstar Program item price.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue when using the Quick Create feature on a Purchase Order.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue with Daily Report showing Trade-ins as purchases and sales.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue affecting the &quot;Set up your catalog&quot; link in the Inventory Summary.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue affecting Billing Agent list visibility.</p></li><li><p>Shortened the Qsite URL link when using shortcodes for SMS notifications and fixed the tracking link directing to Qsite.</p></li></ul>",
